# L3 Parent / Child Context

In an Arbitrum L3 setup, the parent chain is usually an L2, and the child chain is the L3.

```text
parent chain = L2
child chain  = L3
```

This changes the meaning of the same bridge functions.

```text
L2 bridge: L1 <-> L2
L3 bridge: L2 <-> L3
```

## Deposit Context

```text
source chain = L2
destination chain = L3
```

## Withdrawal Context

```text
source chain = L3
destination chain = L2
```
